  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Faith_of_the_Seven\" title=\"Faith of the Seven\"><img alt=\"Star of the Faith.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/9/91/Star_of_the_Faith.svg/50px-Star_of_the_Faith.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/9/91/Star_of_the_Faith.svg/75px-Star_of_the_Faith.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/9/91/Star_of_the_Faith.svg/100px-Star_of_the_Faith.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\">Lorcas<br /><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> the Learned</span></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Poor_Fellows\" title=\"Poor Fellows\"><img alt=\"Poor Fellows.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/c/cd/Poor_Fellows.svg/50px-Poor_Fellows.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/c/cd/Poor_Fellows.svg/75px-Poor_Fellows.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/c/cd/Poor_Fellows.svg/100px-Poor_Fellows.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Alias</th><td>\nLorcas the Learned<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabprince_into_king_-_the_ascension_of_jaehaerys_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabprince_into_king_-_the_ascension_of_jaehaerys_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Poor_Fellows\" title=\"Poor Fellows\">Poor Fellows</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Westeros\" title=\"Westeros\">Westerosi</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Died</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/48_AC\" title=\"48 AC\">48&#160;AC</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabprince_into_king_-_the_ascension_of_jaehaerys_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabprince_into_king_-_the_ascension_of_jaehaerys_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><br />outside <a href=\"/index.php/Oldtown\" title=\"Oldtown\">Oldtown</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabprince_into_king_-_the_ascension_of_jaehaerys_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabprince_into_king_-_the_ascension_of_jaehaerys_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i> (mentioned)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Rise_of_the_Dragon\" title=\"The Rise of the Dragon\">The Rise of the Dragon</a></i> (mentioned)</li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Lorcas the Learned</b> was a member of the <a href=\"/index.php/Poor_Fellows\" title=\"Poor Fellows\">Poor Fellows</a> during the <a href=\"/index.php/Faith_Militant_uprising\" title=\"Faith Militant uprising\">Faith Militant uprising</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Appearance_and_Character\">Appearance and Character</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lorcas_the_Learned&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Appearance and Character\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Lorcas boasted of having committed <i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Seven-Pointed_Star\" title=\"The Seven-Pointed Star\">The Seven-Pointed Star</a></i> to memory.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabprince_into_king_-_the_ascension_of_jaehaerys_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabprince_into_king_-_the_ascension_of_jaehaerys_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> Like Septon <a href=\"/index.php/Moon_(septon)\" title=\"Moon (septon)\">Moon</a>, Lorcas was a big man.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtrotd61.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtrotd61.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lorcas_the_Learned&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Following the death of <a href=\"/index.php/Septon\" title=\"Septon\">Septon</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Moon_(septon)\" title=\"Moon (septon)\">Moon</a>, Lorcas became one of his would-be successors. He conflicted with <a href=\"/index.php/Rob_the_Starvling\" title=\"Rob the Starvling\">Rob the Starvling</a> over the possession of Septon Moon's corpse. Lorcas claimed to have had a <a href=\"/index.php/Vision\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Vision\">vision</a> that Moon would deliver <a href=\"/index.php/Oldtown\" title=\"Oldtown\">Oldtown</a> to his followers, even after his death. Lorcas seized Moon's body from Rob the Starvling, and strapped it atop a <a href=\"/index.php/Horse\" title=\"Horse\">destrier</a> (still naked, bloody, and rotting), to storm the gates of the city. Fewer than a hundred men joined the attack, and most were shot before they even got close to Oldtown's walls. Lorcas was among the few who did reach the walls, and died after being doused with boiling oil or set on fire with burning pitch.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabprince_into_king_-_the_ascension_of_jaehaerys_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabprince_into_king_-_the_ascension_of_jaehaerys_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lorcas_the_Learned&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabprince_into_king_-_the_ascension_of_jaehaerys_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabprince_into_king_-_the_ascension_of_jaehaerys_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabprince_into_king_-_the_ascension_of_jaehaerys_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabprince_into_king_-_the_ascension_of_jaehaerys_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\">1.2</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabprince_into_king_-_the_ascension_of_jaehaerys_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\">1.3</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabprince_into_king_-_the_ascension_of_jaehaerys_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-4\">1.4</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, Prince into King - The Ascension of Jaehaerys I.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtrotd61.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtrotd61.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Rise_of_the_Dragon\" title=\"The Rise o